---
title: Salt-Pepper Chicken & Veggie Fried Rice with Garlic Aioli, Bacon Bits & Coriander
description: Has a rice ever looked this delicious because it’s making our dreams come true. The veggies in the rice are zested with lemon juice and soy sauce for a deep medley of flavours. The chicken is spiced and peppered to perfection so the combination is the stuff of dreams.
